 newspaper and other media accounts.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aCity planningzAsia. 0aLand use, UrbanxGovernment policyzAsia. 0aReal estate developmentxGovernment policyzAsia. 0aReal estate investmentxGovernment policyzAsia. 0aUrban policyzAsia. 4aAsian Studies. 4aGeneral Economics. 4aUrban Studies.  aurban economics, urban real estate, city planning, urban governance, Asian history, real-estate-based urban development in Asia.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Packagez978311064982608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311066587140uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/9781501709715?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501709715423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501709715/original  a978-3-11-064982-6  Asian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Package  a978-3-11-066587-1  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles